This projects implements machines as in
    The Language of Machines: Introduction to Computability and Formal Languages (Floyd and Beigel) 
At the long term I expect to also implement techniques from
    Compilers: Principles, Techniques, and Tools

Build it using
    cmake .
    make

To test it check
    cd the_language_of_machines
    bash run_all.sh

In the_language_of_machines/* there are examples and exercices with some programs for the machines
